release_notes:
This release is a mirror of GA release 2022.10.107.0
 
## Notable updates
- Fixed issue where GUI may still think user is registered after "warp-cli delete" is run
- Decreased warp-diag zip file sizes by 60-80%
 
 
## Known issues
- If you are having issues with upgrading to new beta, please uninstall current app, install the GA version from https://1.1.1.1/ and participate in beta program from Preferences->Advanced.
 
For Zero Trust documentation please see: https://developers.cloudflare.com/cloudflare-one/connections/connect-devices/warp
 
For Consumer documentation please see: https://developers.cloudflare.com/warp-client/
